Note on data: The MIT license above covers the R code only. The raw input data
are official statistics from the German Federal Statistical Office (Destatis,
GENESIS-Online) and the Königsteiner Schlüssel (GWK), redistributed here under
their respective terms with attribution. The CEPII Gravity database is not
redistributed in this repository (see README). Please cite the original data
providers when reusing the data.
